<div class="title">It Has Pros and Cons</div>
<div class="substance">Amphetamines</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Sabrina&Exact=1">Sabrina</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Sabrina. "It Has Pros and Cons: An Experience with Amphetamines (exp93959)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. May 22, 2013. erowid.org/exp/93959</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
